567
00:40:51,790 --> 00:40:53,100
and have a proper talk.

568
00:40:59,100 --> 00:40:59,710
I admit

569
00:41:01,030 --> 00:41:03,030
it was wrong of me to throw a fit
during the show,

570
00:41:07,270 --> 00:41:07,940
but I just

571
00:41:09,270 --> 00:41:10,580
couldn't control myself.

572
