577
00:41:40,350 --> 00:41:42,140
were the most precious part of my life.

578
00:41:46,100 --> 00:41:46,910
From high school

579
00:41:48,460 --> 00:41:49,390
until now,

580
00:41:51,430 --> 00:41:52,350
we grew up together.

581
00:41:56,660 --> 00:41:58,060
We witnessed

582
00:41:58,390 --> 00:42:00,350
all the important moments
in each other's lives.

583
00:42:01,530 --> 00:42:04,210
♪Longing could turn into
staying together forever♪

584
00:42:04,980 --> 00:42:05,620
You

585
00:42:08,430 --> 00:42:09,660
have already become

586
00:42:09,750 --> 00:42:11,270
an inseparable part of my life.

587
00:42:12,490 --> 00:42:16,490
♪Holding you in my arms
just for that one second♪

588
00:42:16,530 --> 00:42:18,730
♪Time pauses forever♪

589
00:42:20,390 --> 00:42:22,580
Even though our love
didn't have a happy ending,

590
00:42:23,330 --> 00:42:25,930
♪From the beginning to the end♪

591
00:42:27,830 --> 00:42:29,830
I still want to be in your life

592
00:42:30,580 --> 00:42:31,940
in some other way,

593
00:42:32,770 --> 00:42:35,270
♪I still remember loving
each other deeply♪

594
00:42:35,270 --> 00:42:37,100
just like we are now,
as client and contractor.

595
00:42:39,710 --> 00:42:41,910
But if you don't want to see me anymore,

596
00:42:45,910 --> 00:42:47,270
once the work is done,

597
00:42:52,440 --> 00:42:53,430
I'll leave from your sight.

598
00:43:01,140 --> 00:43:01,910
No matter what,

599
00:43:03,820 --> 00:43:05,530
