with you as strangers.

600
00:43:09,830 --> 00:43:10,750
Me too.

601
00:43:14,020 --> 00:43:15,500
Then, let's each take a step back

602
00:43:16,750 --> 00:43:18,710
and return to the range we can handle.

603
00:43:18,730 --> 00:43:22,010
♪The overlapping silhouettes
of two people♪

604
00:43:22,210 --> 00:43:24,090
♪At the end of the world♪

605
00:43:24,170 --> 00:43:28,090
♪Holding you in my arms
just for that one second♪

606
00:43:28,130 --> 00:43:30,330
♪Time pauses forever♪

607
00:43:32,790 --> 00:43:34,140
Then, what are we now?

608
00:43:36,100 --> 00:43:37,570
A partner.

609
00:43:37,570 --> 00:43:38,490
♪It turns out♪

610
00:43:38,570 --> 00:43:41,850
♪You've always been a part of my life♪

611
00:43:41,970 --> 00:43:44,610
♪As if you've never left♪

612
00:43:44,610 --> 00:43:47,010
♪I still remember loving
each other deeply♪

613
00:43:47,050 --> 00:43:49,130
♪Searching for what you like♪

614
00:43:49,170 --> 00:43:51,730
♪Getting used to your habits♪

615
00:43:52,290 --> 00:43:54,050
♪The feelings I can't let go the most♪

616
00:43:54,410 --> 00:43:56,930
♪I wonder if you, too♪

617
00:43:56,970 --> 00:43:59,730
