00:45:57,910 --> 00:45:59,310
and also Shen Xingruo's

653
00:45:59,350 --> 00:46:01,270
classmate during her overseas studies.

654
00:46:02,100 --> 00:46:03,790
They also participated

655
00:46:03,790 --> 00:46:05,430
in a show called "Race Against Time".

656
00:46:05,940 --> 00:46:07,940
Many fans shipped for them as a couple,

657
00:46:07,940 --> 00:46:10,350
calling their team
"Rainbow Encounter CP".

658
00:46:12,060 --> 00:46:13,310
What's more,

659
00:46:13,660 --> 00:46:15,140
it seems that Yu Si

660
00:46:15,460 --> 00:46:17,580
is pursuing Xingruo now.

661
00:46:19,270 --> 00:46:19,910
Really?

662
00:46:28,620 --> 00:46:30,100
Director, I have a suggestion.

663
00:46:31,660 --> 00:46:32,239
Go ahead.

664
00:46:33,020 --> 00:46:33,710
I think

665
00:46:34,270 --> 00:46:36,460
