666
00:46:36,980 --> 00:46:38,460
for the upcoming episodes.

667
00:46:39,910 --> 00:46:42,580
After these few episodes,
it's inevitable that the guests

668
00:46:42,580 --> 00:46:44,270
have become dull.

669
00:46:44,710 --> 00:46:45,540
At this moment,

670
00:46:45,870 --> 00:46:48,660
instead of the production team
deliberately arranging something,

671
00:46:49,100 --> 00:46:52,460
it is better to integrate
something new among them

672
00:46:53,020 --> 00:46:56,100
to activate their initiative

673
00:46:56,100 --> 00:46:57,310
and stir things up naturally.

674
00:46:58,500 --> 00:46:59,270
As you can see,

675
00:46:59,750 --> 00:47:01,710
Yu Si and Xingruo's

676
00:47:02,020 --> 00:47:03,310
unexpected outing

677
00:47:03,660 --> 00:47:06,100
has already created some tension

678
00:47:06,100 --> 00:47:07,270
between Mr. Lu and Xingruo.

679
00:47:08,690 --> 00:47:10,390
Between childhood friend
and new contender,

680
00:47:11,020 --> 00:47:11,870
who will she choose?

681
00:47:12,620 --> 00:47:14,870
Isn't this the kind of drama
the audience loves to watch?

682
00:47:17,430 --> 00:47:18,620
But, there's one issue.

683
00:47:19,910 --> 00:47:22,100
Do you think

684
00:47:22,350 --> 00:47:24,390
