685
00:47:25,060 --> 00:47:25,980
It shouldn't.

686
00:47:27,270 --> 00:47:28,580
At the start of filming,

687
00:47:28,910 --> 00:47:29,980
didn't Producer Shen say

688
00:47:30,540 --> 00:47:32,230
she wouldn't interfere with

689
00:47:32,780 --> 00:47:34,020
