694
00:47:42,830 --> 00:47:45,020
I'll work on
getting a female challenger.

695
00:47:45,750 --> 00:47:48,830
This way, in addition
to the "Old Friends Reunion" theme,

696
00:47:48,830 --> 00:47:50,430
we'll have another storyline

