00:49:29,570 --> 00:49:31,650
When Ruo was about two years old,

732
00:49:32,570 --> 00:49:35,170
her family moved to Huize,

733
00:49:35,170 --> 00:49:37,690
and we didn't meet each other for years.

734
00:49:37,690 --> 00:49:40,170
But, fate is

735
00:49:40,170 --> 00:49:41,770
such a wonderful thing.

736
00:49:41,770 --> 00:49:43,050
After all the twists and turns,

737
00:49:43,050 --> 00:49:45,770
people who are destined to be together
